@SmartBets_HostAddress = http://localhost:5160
@ApiKey = your-api-key-here

### Health
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/ping
Accept: application/json

### Countries sync
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/countries/sync
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Leagues sync
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/leagues/sync
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Teams sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/teams/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Full fixtures sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Upcoming fixtures sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/sync-upcoming?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Match winner odds sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025&marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Standings sync for one league-season
POST {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/standings/sync?leagueId=39&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}

### Legacy fixtures list with filters
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures?leagueId=39&season=2025&state=Upcoming&direction=asc
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Paged fixtures query for frontend
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/query?leagueId=39&season=2025&state=Finished&from=2025-08-01&to=2025-08-31&page=1&pageSize=20&direction=desc
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Team-centric fixtures query using API team id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/query?teamId=33&state=Live&page=1&pageSize=10
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Fixture detail by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456?marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Latest fixture odds by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456/odds?marketName=Match%20Winner&latestOnly=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Best fixture odds by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/fixtures/123456/best-odds?marketName=Match%20Winner
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Odds endpoint by API fixture id
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/odds?apiFixtureId=123456&marketName=Match%20Winner&latestOnly=true
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Sync freshness overview
GET {{SmartBets_HostAddress}}/api/sync-status?activeOnly=true&season=2025
X-API-KEY: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json
